        td 使用方法
      tr
        td
          div(class="block" id="block2")
            div(class="subsubtitle" id="subsub1") 上传skill data
            div(class="subblock" id="subblock1")
              p 1.在浏览器的书签上登录下面的代码
              p For GITADORA Tri-Boost Re:EVOLVE
              div(class="script") javascript:void(!function(d){var s=d.createElement("script");s.type="text/javascript";s.src="//gitadora-skill-viewer.herokuapp.com/js/uploaddata_tbre.js";d.head.appendChild(s);}(document));
              p For GITADORA Tri-Boost
